Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說過這裡的夏天很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會這麼熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季才剛過\N熱成這樣太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想裝台冷氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生病了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是生病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點中暑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中暑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是指天氣太熱而沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能老是這麼懶散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正補習班也有冷氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是早點去讀書好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，招待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（全館空調系統檢測通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在下一節課前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷氣就會修好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在出個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人答得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會我請大家吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要草莓牛奶冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，要答得出來才有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答題的學生要由我來選
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來回答看看\N課本第25頁的第3題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最基礎的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉例說明好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常用到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼熱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為冷氣壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你弄壞的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干我什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看起來很鬱卒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你今天有沒有空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在打工前有點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一節英文課的筆記\N能不能借我抄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我請你吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的字也未免太潦草了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個像顛倒音符的是什麼字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是 U 啦， U
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也叫 U 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正內容是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將英語課本\N第158頁第六行開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯成英文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we shouid piaced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among the causes\Nof happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or among the causes\Nof unhappiness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may perhaps be regarded\Nas a dreadfui question
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯\NThere is certainiy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了，絲茉茉\NThere is certainiy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你這裡抄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉頭腦真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉裝有英日翻譯軟體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能幫你出題目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠻方便的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想借絲茉茉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是報答你借我筆記
