Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有提到\N明天可能會有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐給的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得聞到這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓人有夏天的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫作夏天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說季節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣熱是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣冷是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣溫暖是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚會是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份，竟然把人家給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是忘了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說是夏天的錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一場夏日的回憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有玩弄妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的，認真的，誠心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住一晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是本須和的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有男生房間的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼自己跑進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎，別在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀\Nちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…妳叫ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是孺子可教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝給他醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師妳才剛喝過不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整理好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說要住一晚是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是什麼行不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼做比較好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法熬到天亮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣更不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是願意讓我住一晚囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對我做什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師妳打算喝這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，很平常，很平常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹教過我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個形狀怎麼形容？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在笑的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是好想當喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小學？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳原本想當小學老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，原本是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我老公說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小學要是當了班導師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會忙到沒時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以反對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被老公反對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得電腦比較可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人類比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟電腦在一起比較快樂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡好笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以請妳下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該停了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“國王遊戲”很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我被命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你籤運那麼差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就繼續玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像個男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽籤的時候乾脆點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ也抽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該做點刺激的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺激？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到二號的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻國王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請拿到二號的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是幾號？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又好像有點可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩親親囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的眼神已經不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要親囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是本須和的電腦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託不要嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有精神起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對沒有想歪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是想其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砰一聲倒下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來我睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會吵醒ちぃ的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好真實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經天亮了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只穿內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在夢裡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…\N早安，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，臉濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，妳那個穿著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒欺負你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欺負…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟第一次要給喜歡的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和你還是很純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是天氣熱脫下衣服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟本須和都是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全部看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算一般尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹是一般的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，這個不必記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我盥洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有牙刷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一開始就打算來借住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就打算在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…為什麼妳要來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為膽小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經出門了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這位上禮拜在海邊見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，敝姓清水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，補習班的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天功課一定進步不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直嘆氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能被她誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在在意那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是真誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下次去幫你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這確實讓人傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被誤會跟我在交往的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是老師比較傷腦筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師在煩惱些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以說給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以找我談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟我聽到的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個跟現在說的無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真累人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出門了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很睏的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天清水老師突然來我房間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始點名…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師，點名就不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，翻開第26頁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是慘斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保一副可怕的表情\N一句話也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我為他操心\N打工時老出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還要被雨淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早點睡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸口為什麼濕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是因為下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子真是一點也不老實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不老實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉上的妝都糊掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的女人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子最可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會被人看見喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在補習班教書的是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在補習班讀書的是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師是補習班老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師\N跟補習班學生抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個補習班學生是新保
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師是有夫之婦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.60,0:24:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，什麼都不做」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來也只能這樣
